title: Suzi Katz-1991 folky singer/songwriter EAC FLAC
description:
picked this CD up years ago in a cutout bin at a used CD store. I fell in love with it on first play. After years of just "listening" I'm switching gears and will be performing "The People" a week from today with a percussionist (I'm doing the vocals). 

Suzi Katz is designing web sites for a living (and does a great, great job by the way) out of Asheville, NC. Rumor has it that she didn't like traveling and as a result her two CDs did not reach the exposure they deserved. 

This CD in the category of "if I were stranded on a desert island with only ten CDs... this would be one of them". *(Amazon review)
